Interface ResponseFilterContext

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RawResponse
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RawResponseImpl

    public interface ResponseFilterContext
    Allows one to modify HTTP Response Headers.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
